quran[8]{c,v,t}:
  95,1,"M wẽen ne Tɩɩn(Kɑnkɑmɑ) la zaytʋʋne."
  95,2,"La M wẽen ne Sɩɩnɑɑ'ʋ tãngã."
  95,3,"La M wẽen ne tẽn-kãngã (Mɑkɑ) sẽn yaa bas-m-yam tẽngã."
  95,4,"Sɩd la hakɩɩka, Tõnd naana ninsaala, ne yagd sẽn yɩɩd sõmblem."
  95,5,"Rẽ poorẽ D lεbs-a lame tẽngr rãmbã fãa tẽngre."
  95,6,"Ralla neb nins sẽn kõ-b sɩda, la b tʋm sẽn sõmbã. Ad be ne-bɑ, rolb sẽn pa wãagde."
  95,7,"La bõe n kɩt tɩ fo yagsd Rolbã rɑɑre, fo sẽn yã A tõogã loogr poorẽ?"
  95,8,"Rẽ yĩnga pa Wẽnd n yɩɩd bʋʋdbã fãa ne bʋʋd minim?"
